月与斯威夫特一起在温布利演出了三场门票全部售完的演出</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-holly-humberstone-suki-waterhouse-and-more-confirmed-to-support-taylor-swift-for-final-wembley-eras-shows-3781049">斯威夫特本月将在体育场举行另外五场约会</a>，索菲亚·伊塞拉（8 月 15 日）、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/holly-humberstone">霍莉·亨伯斯通</a>（16 岁）、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maisie-peters">麦茜·彼得斯</a>（19 岁）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">雷伊</a>（20 岁）也将加入其中。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/suki-waterhouse-sparklemuffin-new-album-eras-tour-1235079134/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>采访时，沃特豪斯畅谈了参加盛大的“Eras Tour”现象的感受。</p><p> “我一直在梦想、梦想、梦想这一切的发生，”她告诉媒体。</p><p> “我表现得非常努力。所以当[我发现]时，我想，是的，梦想可以成真。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-SkB9AJHZm/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenod